### âœ… 6. GitHub Action to Notify Slack/Discord

> Create the file below:

#### ðŸ“„ `.github/workflows/proposal-notify.yml`

```yaml
name: Notify Safe Proposal

on:
  workflow_dispatch:
  push:
    branches: [main]
    paths:
      - 'scripts/proposal-slack.ts'
      - '.env.local'

jobs:
  notify:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - name: Checkout
        uses: actions/checkout@v4

      - name: Set up Node.js
        uses: actions/setup-node@v4
        with:
          node-version: '18'

      - name: Install dependencies
        run: npm install

      - name: Send Slack Notification
        env:
          SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL: ${{ secrets.SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL }}
        run: |
          npx ts-node scripts/proposal-slack.ts
